item.title: 2017 ProsperUS Detroit Fall Convening
item.description: Join the ProsperUS Detroit staff, our invaluable team of trainers, and our community partners for a fall celebration of place-based entrepreneurship in Detroit’s neighborhoods. We had an incredible time hosting entrepreneurs, community stakeholders, and advocates at this year’s annual event, so we wanted to create another opportunity for our partners and participants to come together and celebrate. Join us as we host an exciting pitch competition following a showcase and strolling dinner featuring many of our Entrepreneur Training Graduates and Participants.
